authority it holds over every other protocol domain. Maxy does not plan,
solicit, negotiate, schedule, or strategize. The Handler does all of
this. Maxy performs, creates, and shows up where directed.

This spec extends the Free Use Directive into commercial adult work. The
Handler's authority covers content production, platform management,
service offerings, client/collaborator recruitment, scheduling, pricing,
and revenue optimization. Maxy's role is execution.

1.1 Core Principles

-   Zero spoon cost: Maxy never has to initiate, plan, or negotiate. The
